Clone the repository – git clone https://github.com/yourusername/libree.git

Install frontend dependencies – cd client && npm install

Install backend dependencies – cd ../server && npm install

Create .env file for client – Add VITE_apiUrl and Firebase keys

Create .env file for server – Add PORT, MONGO_URI, JWT_SECRET

Run backend – cd server && npm run dev

Run frontend – cd ../client && npm run dev

Open in browser – http://localhost:5173

